c: 5
v: 68
t: "Ithi, Oh Bantu bencwadi! Animile phezulu kwalutho kuze kube nenza ngendlela eyala ngayo iTora neVangeli nalokho okwehliselwa phansi kunina (iQur’an) okuvela eNkosini yenu futhi ngempela lokho okwembulwa kuwena okuvela eNkosini yakho kuyokwandisa eningini labo ukona nokungakholwa ngakho-ke ungaphatheki kabi ngenxa yabantu abangakholwa"